1.body: Git Source Authors: Fernando Martinelli - @fernandomartinelli, Sergio Yuhjtman - @sergioyuhjtman, Daniel Fernandez - @dmf7z Exponentiation and logarithm functions for 18 decimal fixed point numbers (both base and exponent/argument). forked from https://github.com/balancer/balancer-v2-monorepo/blob/599b0cd8f744e1eabef3600d79a2c2b0aea3ddcb/pkg/solidity-utils/contracts/math/LogExpMath.sol Exponentiation and logarithm with arbitrary bases (x^y and log_x(y)) are implemented by conversion to natural exponentiation and logarithm (where the base is Euler's number).
1.title: LogExpMath
